{
  "stem": "11844.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a big, German construction company and they were doing fortifications at the-- to build the Atlantic Wall as a defense against a possible invasion.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was working for them as a guy to get Dutch laborer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he got lots of young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were hired by the Organization Todt-- Jews and non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once they came to France, they worked with the Organization Todt for a few weeks, close to the Spanish border, the Gulf of Biscay.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Du-- The Dutch-- the non-Jewish boys-- went to Spain, and went from there to England.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Jewish boys went from there to Spain, and went from there with [INAUDIBLE] from Spain to-- to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, I want to help you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, well, I don't think you have the capability to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, well, he got me in touch with somebody else, and they tested me how good I am.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, there was rationing-- food rationing-- in Holland at the time, which was very, very tight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you needed a document, which was called 'eine stamkaarte.' And with that, you had to go to distribution offices where you got coupons for milk and butter and meat and-- very little.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the-- all the people who lived underground, Jews and non-Jews, they had no document for food rationing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that one girl-- her name was Laura Doller-- Jewish girl-- she said, OK, we can use you for the following.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here are 80 or 100-- I forgot-- 80 or 100 stamkaarten.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you go to various distribution offices and get food rations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But don't give anyone more than five or six.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only five or six.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I go to the first distribution office, you know, with my big briefcase full of stamkaarten.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
